OL,7,FOne of the standout elements of
OL,8,FBritain's Challenger 2 tank which is
OL,9,Fbeing deployed to Ukraine is a kettle
OL,10,Fthat allows for tea on the go,
OL,11,Faccording to a commander.
OL,13,FIt sounds like a quintessentially
OL,14,FBritish feature to satiate soldiers'
OL,15,Fthirst for a brew wherever they are in
OL,16,Fthe world, but the "boiling vessel" is
OL,17,Fimportant in maintaining the morale and
OL,18,Fwellbeing of the crew, said Justin
OL,19,FCrump, a former British Army commander
OL,20,Fwho used the Challenger 2 during
OL,21,Foperations in Iraq in 2003-4.
OL,3,CBest thing about Challenger 2 tank is
OL,4,C'kettle' for making tea, says ex
OL,5,CBritish Army commander
